com.whirvis.jraknet.protocol

Class ConnectionType

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.whirvis.jraknet.protocol.ConnectionType

  • public class ConnectionType
extends java.lang.Object
    Used to signify which implementation of the RakNet protocol is being used by a connection. Keep in mind that this functionality has no guarantees to function completely, as it is completely dependent on the implementation to implement this feature.
    Author:
    Trent "Whirvis" Summerlin
